{"tid":83454,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如何捱過生離死別？","createTime":"2017-01-16T17:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T17:15:18.000Z","uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9270ecfa077d15d9df3e70740f91299a65e3b3d","tid":83454,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:55:18.000Z","msg":"臨近新年先至咁，早前去探病情況明明有好轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d6fdcec763da26760a7fce11dc60f67c37b04de","tid":83454,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:04:53.000Z","msg":"唔識，幫你唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過加油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a42c9cbff57afe2cf3b9c1aa33192e2261e512","tid":83454,"uid":19095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:06:43.000Z","msg":"逝者已去<br />\n好好珍惜眼前人啦<br />\n唔好再比自己有後悔既機會"},{"pid":"730b7b39434aad8c402ba20b369839582a2e1dee","tid":83454,"uid":19095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:09:54.000Z","msg":"我都已經兩年冇慶祝過農曆新年喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最親既人突然唔係到係會好難受<br />\n但過去已經補救唔到<br />\n每個人都有離開既一日<br />\n可以好突然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申我每日都會諗一次佢地把聲"},{"pid":"255a860b9bcf7dfefb90992e60a2ec561832faa1","tid":83454,"uid":66234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:11:10.000Z","msg":"你根本就無選擇<br />\n只可以接受<br />\n然後繼續活下去"},{"pid":"91e17f4b927f66d44db698e13c3d11ca276dae3b","tid":83454,"uid":39274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:12:08.000Z","msg":"早2日先有親人過身<br />\n生離死別 人之常情<br />\n你要接受依個係改變唔到既命運<br />\n如果佢病既時候係痛苦 咁對佢黎講都算係解脫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97499af9284846ef6b536f3f2178722a70019ebe","tid":83454,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:12:51.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7af8255210725225ac6d21d04f87afe5d2208de","tid":83454,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T20:58:27.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0c5b92294f1bc3501450c483a9e6ab5e58b5df","tid":83454,"uid":40931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T21:33:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早2日先有親人過身<br />\n生離死別 人之常情<br />\n你要接受依個係改變唔到既命運<br />\n如果佢病既時候係痛苦 咁對佢黎講都算係解脫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加油加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913cfd07211fedf4891f3f33095478f1f929bddc","tid":83454,"uid":40931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T21:34:18.000Z","msg":"樓主 珍惜眼前人 唔好俾自己錯過對家人好嘅機會已經好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5c0c9328c3207e9b5b7c0f72c5abd09bf228ed","tid":83454,"uid":8569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:21:57.000Z","msg":"捱過左(好似係)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係時間問題 不過有後遺症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b23fea69f5ad80e28e1c65860e70a36467ebef4","tid":83454,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:29:05.000Z","msg":"感謝上面各位回覆<br />\n<br />\n我同過身個親人無咁親，所以件事發生左之後情緒無咁強烈<br />\n但係聽講之前我婆婆去探病成日喊到訓唔到覺<br />\n我份人比較不善辭令，上到婆婆屋企探佢真係唔敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10af2d06e0dff110528d876040e749b22cfbc1f1","tid":83454,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早2日先有親人過身<br />\n生離死別 人之常情<br />\n你要接受依個係改變唔到既命運<br />\n如果佢病既時候係痛苦 咁對佢黎講都算係解脫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加油加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去探病見佢瘦左幾個碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5aeaa02b9181eb50905189661b35084fcfc398","tid":83454,"uid":39274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:15:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>早2日先有親人過身<br />\n生離死別 人之常情<br />\n你要接受依個係改變唔到既命運<br />\n如果佢病既時候係痛苦 咁對佢黎講都算係解脫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加油加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去探病見佢瘦左幾個碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加油啦 做人向前望 最親既人都有走既一日<br />\n只係早定遲 錫多啲係你身邊既人啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}